Tata Motors — Quick Take
Company Overview: Tata Motors is India's largest commercial vehicle maker and a major passenger vehicle player, with global scale via Jaguar Land Rover (JLR), its UK-based luxury subsidiary. The business spans three segments: India commercial vehicles (CV), India passenger vehicles (PV, including a fast-growing EV arm), and JLR.
